					"body": "Hello, \r\n\r\nThanks for sharing your thoughts. This would be a nice addition to our platform. For that, this needs to be approved by our selection committee. We will let you know if and when we will integrate this into our platform. It is appreciated if you have any further reference to this feature in native platform. \r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nSharif.",
